longBusinessSummary: Enterprise Development Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated business software solutions in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. It operates through Software Business and Other segments. The company provides software maintenance and other services; and sells software and other products. It is also involved in the money lending and security trading activities. The company was formerly known as Tai-I International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Enterprise Development Holdings Limited in May 2011. Enterprise Development Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
